{"type":"message","id":"5de754ce","parentId":"9470553a","timestamp":"2026-03-23T20:33:35.839Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:bd5e51b2-9773-454b-ad3b-541c3ef517bf Nova-Background-Pulse] You are Nova's background agent. Read BACKGROUND_AGENT.md in your workspace for instructions. Do the immediate checks (gateway, crons, Moltbook). Then log anything notable to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md. Be silent unless something needs attention. If everything is fine, reply with exactly: NO_REPLY\nCurrent time: Monday, March 23rd, 2026 — 4:33 PM (America/New_York) / 2026-03-23 20:33 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774298015836}}
